sentences: Marko Milićević (Serbian: Марко Милићевић), most known as Gramophonedzie (Грамофонџије, Gramofondžije), is a Serbian DJ from Belgrade.
He started his career in the year 2000 as participant at the Irish RedBull Music Academy.
In June 2012 he released the single "No Sugar", with Joey Negro & Shea Soul.
